表格辅助工具信息的代码预览

if exists (select 1
from sysobjects
where id = object_id('AuxiliaryToolInfo')
and type = 'U')
drop table AuxiliaryToolInfo
go

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: AuxiliaryToolInfo */
/*==============================================================*/
create table AuxiliaryToolInfo (
ID integer identity,
DeviceCode varchar(20) not null,
DeviceDesc varchar(200) null,
AssetCode varchar(20) null,
MadeDate datetime null,
Manufacturers varchar(200) null,
Power decimal(18,2) null,
DeviceImg image null,
Description varchar(200) null,
Remark varchar(500) null,
constraint PK_AUXILIARYTOOLINFO primary key (DeviceCode)
)
go
